	(3136,389,'introduction_title','Passionate about connecting people with great investment opportunities'),
	(3137,389,'_introduction_title','field_60d30079eddae'),
	(3138,389,'introduction_text','Virgin Islands Collection is the one-stop online platform from the experts who have brought you Virgin Islands Property &amp; Yacht. We have toured the most exclusive homes in the Virgin Islands, sailed on the most luxurious yachts, and visited every bay, mountain, and beach from Anegada to Zion Hill. For the past thirteen years, we have been a trusted real estate and sailing industry partner.\r\n\r\nSo we decided to use our years of experience to provide a service to you, the discernable buyer of a stunning home or majestic yacht. We will help you navigate the ins and outs of the Virgin Islands property and yacht markets and how to jump through all the hoops necessary to realize your dream of living and sailing in the Virgin Islands. No other platform has the comprehensive experience, access, and expertise that we have. Before making your investment into the Virgin Islands, a consultation with us is necessary.\r\n\r\nOn this site, you will be able to research how to begin a property search, how to buy a yacht, and how to finance your endeavors. You will learn about the rules and regulations of the Virgin Islands as well as the seasons, climate, and sailing destinations. You can explore each island in great detail to see which one is most suited to your unique personality. You can virtually visit each marina and harbor to plan your future visits. We are here to simplify the process and save you time by providing everything you need under one umbrella  Virgin Islands Collection.'),
	(3139,389,'_introduction_text','field_60d30079eddbd'),
	(3140,389,'feature_items_0_title','Our Story'),
	(3141,389,'_feature_items_0_title','field_60d3008445a82'),
	(3142,389,'feature_items_0_text','The goal of Virgin Islands Collection, created by Parlance Media Limited, is to promote the Virgin Islands as a place to invest.\r\nWith extensive real estate knowledge, Parlance Media has been showcasing beautiful homes and yachts since 2003.\r\n\r\nParlance Media understands the real estate and yacht markets in the Virgin Islands, but is not a real estate agent or yacht broker. Parlance Media is a trusted, neutral partner with years of expertise whose aim is to help you to navigate the ins and outs of purchasing or renting a property or purchasing a yacht.\r\n\r\nBased in the British Virgin Islands, Parlance Media is passionate about the BVI real estate and sailing industries. By creating Virgin Islands Collection, we are looking to make the process of searching for dream home or yacht easier for the buyer while also providing a trusted platform for the real estate and yacht sales industries. \r\n'),
